    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a deep, mirror-like paint finish completely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather is supple and crease-free, and every button and switch retains its crisp, factory feel. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service history detailing every preventative maintenance milestone performed by master technicians. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of pampering. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously maintained investment that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it was first delivered.",
      "price": 48500.0,
