      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly flawless shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and not a single scratch or dent to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
