    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system that remains in peak operational spec. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a factory variable M differential lock. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement, addressing the critical structural points of the chassis. The suspension retains its original kinematics with fresh bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and lateral stability expected of the M-division. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a pristine interior, this is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
